  "title": "Tapping for \"this isn't for me\"",
  "subtitle": "A five-minute script for releasing the belief that financial abundance is available to others but not to you.",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 16 of Rebecca's MONEY program. The script targets the specific belief that money, success, or financial freedom works for other people but somehow skips you.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Day 16 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025), \"Let go of 'others can, not me'.\" Tapping framework: Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 16 of the MONEY program. The script targets the exclusion belief: the feeling of being on the outside of abundance, watching other people receive what you tell yourself is not for you.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "how EFT tapping works",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Karate chop",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though I believe money happens for others but not for me, I deeply and completely accept myself.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though I feel left out of abundance, I deeply and completely accept myself.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though I fear I'll always be the exception, I deeply and completely accept myself.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Tapping round",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Eyebrow:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I see other people making money.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Side of eye:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I wonder why it skips me.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Under eye:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I think I'm unlucky or missing something.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Under nose:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I feel stuck on the outside looking in.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Chin:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I've told myself it's just not for me.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Collarbone:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I feel envy and frustration.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Under arm:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I'm ready to release that belief.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Top of head:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I don't want to live as the exception.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Reframe to positive",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
